1️⃣ Tank Formasyonları (Tanks)

    Line → Tank – Tank – Tank

    Wedge → Tank – Tank – Tank

    Vee → Tank – Tank – Tank

    Echelon Left → Tank – Tank – Tank

    Echelon Right → Tank – Tank – Tank

    Column → Tank – Tank – Tank – Tank

    Staggered Column → Tank – Tank – Tank – Tank

    Herringbone → Tank – Tank – Tank – Tank

2️⃣ Piyade Formasyonları (Infantry - Only APC or IFV)

    Squad Column → IFV – IFV – IFV

    Diamond Formation → IFV – IFV – IFV – IFV

    Ranger File → APC – APC – APC

    Staggered File → APC – APC – APC

    Line Formation → APC – APC – APC

3️⃣ Jet Formasyonları (Fighter or Bomber Jets)

    Finger Four → Jet – Jet – Jet – Jet

    Line Abreast → Jet – Jet – Jet

    Wedge → Jet – Jet – Jet

    Echelon Left → Jet – Jet – Jet

    Echelon Right → Jet – Jet – Jet

    Vic Formation → Jet – Jet – Jet

    Trail Formation → Jet – Jet – Jet

4️⃣ Helikopter Formasyonları (Attack or Transport Helicopters)

    Staggered Trail → Helicopter – Helicopter – Helicopter

    Diamond Formation → Helicopter – Helicopter – Helicopter – Helicopter

    Column Formation → Helicopter – Helicopter – Helicopter

    Echelon Left → Helicopter – Helicopter – Helicopter

    Echelon Right → Helicopter – Helicopter – Helicopter

    V Formation → Helicopter – Helicopter – Helicopter

5️⃣ İHA Formasyonları (Drones)

    Swarm Formation → Drone – Drone – Drone – Drone

    Grid Formation → Drone – Drone – Drone

    Line Formation → Drone – Drone – Drone

6️⃣ Savaş Gemisi Formasyonları (Warships)

    Line Abreast → Destroyer – Destroyer – Destroyer

    Echelon → Destroyer – Destroyer – Destroyer

    Column Formation → Cruiser – Cruiser – Cruiser

    Staggered Column → Frigate – Frigate – Frigate

7️⃣ Denizaltı Formasyonları (Submarines)

    Wolfpack Formation → Submarine – Submarine – Submarine

    Trail Formation → Submarine – Submarine – Submarine

    Line Abreast → Submarine – Submarine – Submarine